Question: Is the bowl to the right of the apple made of metal?

Reference Answer: No, the bowl is made of glass.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/2369690.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='apple')
IMAGE0=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='bowl')
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What material is the bowl made of?')
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'metal' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
